snippet.title: MC STΔN -  NUSTA PAISA  (Official Music Video) | 2023
snippet.description:
Jayega kaam ko, toh khayega shaam ko - MC Stan

Stream "Nusta Paisa": https://mcstan.lnk.to/NustaPaisa

Lyrics: 
Nusta paisa 
Phir kya bolti company 
Sabko Psy

Nusta Paisa, Nusta Paisa 
Nusta Paisa, Nusta Paisa 
Nusta Paisa, Nusta Paisa
Nusta Paisa, Nusta Paisa
                   
Meku test mat kar, mein marta ghar dar
Ye diss karra gandu, iska vishaych karta 
Teku dikhna pasand hai re bro, mein shaat nai dikhta 
Mala diss karto aai ghalaya, rukh tere pech likhta 

Mein abhi bade bade logo me, uthta baithta 
Aur tu shemde kider toh pan, fukte baithta
Teko score karne paise nai, mein haste chuthta
Meko malum hai re bro, tu meku copy karta

Arrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrr
Tu phele se kele, bhonda dikhta 
Teku phele pan bola tha, tu bhonda likhta 
Fir kya kaaju pista, aeedha gand me ghusta 
Mein sirf gaane likhta, ann sirf notaa ginta

Tu mera fan nai hai bruh, lekin show pe dikhta
Tu like karta lavde photo khudka 
Mein nai marta sutta 
Mein meri maa ki sunnta 
Teku kon nai sunnta
Ann tu kya pan sunnta 

Tu classes k bhar rukh k, madhiya dhoondta 
Mein carti sunnta, ann tu g** sunnta 
Tu dhating karta, ann mein shooting karta
Mein phele ke dost log se, baat nai karta

Tu hai balish buddi, mein shartir ladka 
Tu hate karta meku, aur mein party karta 
1 week me 3 4 bar, shopping karta
Tu ladki log ke number se, message karta

Teku malum meri capacity 
Mein marte chutha matlab 
!! appa !!
Mi haanat soot to 
Pucchi wani tondacha, tu kai pan bolto 
Tumcha aai cha puccha, tumchya gang lach kolto

Arey call uchal ki shattu ji, stanny boltoy
Kiti vela bollo Tula Nadi nako lagu
Ayee D yho aplay la, vadiuu boltoy
Ghalun takal Tula, svata stanny boltoy

Tumlog ye jo karre na, usko planning bolte hai
Logo ko tum bolne do, woh log kya bhi bolte
Mi aai zavto one side, isleye stanny bolte 
Opp la deun taku, ye kai padri 
Ghosta ae

Nusta Paisa, Nusta Paisa 
Nusta Paisa, Nusta Paisa 
Mera paisa mere jaisa 
Iska paisa uska paisa

Nusta Paisa, Nusta Paisa 
Nusta Paisa, Nusta Paisa 
Nusta Paisa, Nusta Paisa
Iska paisa uska paisa 

Tadiwala road, tadi peeta mera homie
Phatki nikla mera khas, mera kattar homie 
Phele kaise thi woh, meku milke change hogayi
Meku pasand nai hai drama, aur woh daily roti 

Only fans unki ban gayeli hai, rozi roti
Squat marke tu hogayeli kitni patli
Mere saath poora india, meri hawa hogayi
Mein bhi rehta teri jaga pe, toh jalan hoti

Shhhhhhhhhhhhhh !!!!

Lafde hogaye mere uss din , daru biru pk
Aage jaana chahte log, mein jana chahta peeche 
Ghumayega mein ek ko, sablog hojayege peeche 
Bich me tere Homie ka, gir gayela wicket

Smoke karu teku jaisa pop smoke vishayyy
Focus karu paise pe, aati uss se bitches
Haath chodho sirf, jab bhi opps log dikhe
Pull up karu shitt, jab bhi cops log dikhe

Yede ki ko woh lera tha, maine bola theek haiiiiiiiii
Ayeeeeee!!! 
SADHU KO JADDU? 
Sabko PSY  
Phir kya bolti company 

Nusta Paisa, Nusta Paisa 
Nusta Paisa, Nusta Paisa 
Mera paisa mere jaisa 
Iska paisa uska paisa

Nusta Paisa, Nusta Paisa 
Nusta Paisa, Nusta Paisa 
Nusta Paisa, Nusta Paisa 
Iska paisa uska paisa

Stay Connected ✅ 

Follow Mc Stan:
INSTAGRAM -  https://www.instagram.com/m___c___stan/
HINDI RECORDS - https://www.instagram.com/hindi_records/

Singe / Performer: MC Stan ( Official baap )
Music Composer: MC Stan 
Author / Lyrics: MC Stan
Prod. by MC STΔN

snippet.title: Jawan: Not Ramaiya Vastavaiya | Shah Rukh Khan | Atlee | Anirudh | Nayanthara | Vishal D | Shilpa R
snippet.description:
Get ready to groove like never before as "Not Ramaiya Vastavaiya", the latest dance track from the highly-anticipated Atlee directorial, Jawan, is out now. The film stars Shah Rukh Khan, Vijay Sethupathi, Nayanthara, and Deepika Padukone (in a special appearance) and is set to release in cinemas on September 7, 2023, in Hindi, Tamil, and Telugu!

#NotRamaiyaVastavaiya out now!

♪Full Song Available on♪ 
JioSaavn: https://bit.ly/3srnLI5
Spotify: https://bit.ly/3ssmbG1
Hungama: https://bit.ly/3OW4upT
Apple Music: https://bit.ly/3OYPyau
Amazon Prime Music: https://bit.ly/44vEozG
Wynk: https://bit.ly/3L0roLy
Resso: https://bit.ly/47UA7Zy
YouTube Music: https://bit.ly/3OWNbov

Music Credits:
Language - Hindi
Song Title - Not Ramaiya Vastavaiya 
Album / Movie - Jawan
Composed by Anirudh Ravichander
Lyrics - Kumaar
Vocals - Anirudh Ravichander, Vishal Dadlani & Shilpa Rao
Choreographer - Vaibhavi Merchant 

Composed, Arranged & Programmed by Anirudh Ravichander
Keyboard, Synth & Rhythm Programmed by Anirudh Ravichander
Whistle - Satish Raghunathan
Tabla - MT Aditya
Additional Rhythm Programmed by Shashank Vijay
Additional Keyboard Programmed by Arish-Pradeep PJ

Music Advisor - Ananthakrrishnan
Creative Consultant - Sajith Satya
Music Editor - Harish Ram L H
Recorded at Albuquerque Records, Chennai. Engineered by Srinivasan M, Shivakiran S, Rajesh Kannan, Jishnu Vijayan
YRF Studios, Mumbai, Engineered by Vijay Dayal & Chinmay
Mixed by Vinay Sridhar & Srinivasan M at Albuquerque Records, Chennai
Mastered by Luca Pretolesi at Studio DMI, Las Vegas Assisted by Alistair Pintus 
Music Coordinator - Velavan B

Lyrics:

Dance with me now I can’t break away
Aaj sari fikreiin tu shake away
Shake away
Dil thirakta dance wale groove pe
Nachun mai to step mera vekh ve

Vekh ve
Aaj sare kaam kal pe talke
Tak dhina dhin nache jayein taal pe
Disko jaz blues sare bhoolke
Desi wale geet pe tu jhoolke
Pehle kiya chaiya chaiya re
Ab kar tha tha thaiyya
Ramiya vasta vaiya..!
Antra

Sama mazedar hua houle houle
Thoda nashedar hua
Man ye dole
Aaj koi nachta hua sa jadu
Sar pe swar hua
Dil ye bole
Doobi khushiyon mein
Raat apni jabse suraj dhala
Chodh sharmana aaj nachle pair chakkle zara

Pahle kiya chaiya chaiiya re
Ab kar tata thaiya
Ramiya vasta vaiyaa..!


___________________________________
Enjoy & stay connected with us!

👉 Like us on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/tseriesmusic
👉 Follow us on X: https://twitter.com/tseries
👉 Follow us on Instagram: http://bit.ly/InstagramTseries

snippet.description:

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada

snippet.title: Rakesh Barot | Mara Veera | મારા વિરા | Rajal Barot | Raksha Bandhan Song | ગુજરાતી ગીત 2023
snippet.description:
"મારા વિરા"...તમારી સમક્ષ રજૂ કરીએ છીએ રાકેશ બારોટ અને રજલ બારોટ નું નવું ગુજરાતી રક્ષા બંધન ગીત. ભાઈ અને બહેનની ભાવનાત્મક વાર્તા 💓! માત્ર  @SaregamaGujarati પર

Listen to the best of Rakesh Barot songs only on Saregama Gujarati !
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLUzteH3czVO5WMxyPrP2RWK4MMHuCKLwL

Title : Mara Veera
Singer : Rakesh Barot, Rajal Barot
Producer : Red Velvet Cinema 
Artist : Rakesh Barot, Rajal Barot
Co Aartist : Durva Barot 
Kunj Barot.nishit Nayak
Music :ravi & Rahul
Lyrice : Chandu Raval
Dop : Dhruv Bhatiya
Editing : Montu Rajput .dhruv Bhatiya
Director - Vishnu Thakor (Adalaj)
Production : Amar Panchal, Manthan Panchal.mehul
Makeup  : Hashmukh Limabachiya.
Hair : Gayatree
Technical Support: Jenish Talaviya 
Sport Boy : Shailesh.
Light : Jitubhai.kiran
Floor Music Avenger : Sunil Kachhiya

અન્ય OTT પ્લેટફોર્મ પર આ ગીતનો આનંદ માણો 🎶
Wynk https://tinyurl.com/2p8vc4za
Hungama https://tinyurl.com/7prvjc8y
Amazon https://tinyurl.com/5xr7nyad
Spotify https://tinyurl.com/3n3b4k4c
Resso https://tinyurl.com/ydt295rj
Gaana https://tinyurl.com/3v5ttfy4
Youtube Music https://tinyurl.com/4xybx486

Lyrics:
હું બેની મારી નારે ભીંજાવશો આંખડી રે......... આંખડી રે....... આંખડી રે
બેની મારી પારકી.... બેની મારી પારકી રે
યે બેની મારી નારે ભીંજાવશો આંખડી રે....
હરખ આયો વીરા તને બાંધતા રાખડી રે
હે ઓહુ તારા..... ઓહુ તારા.....ઓહું તારા....
કાળજા ના કટકા કરે ચાર ઓહું તારા (૨)
બેની મારી નારે ભીંજાવશો આંખડી રે
હો મને હરખ થયો વીરા તને બાંધતા રાખડી રે

હું તારા વિના વીરા કોણ હતું મારે મારા કારણે યે ભઈલા દુઃખ વેઠયું ભારે 
એ મારી ઉંમર બેની તને લાગી જાય દુઃખનો વાયરો તને કોઈ દાડે ના વાય (૨)
હો વીરા તું તો મારા જીવતરની લાકડી રે.... લાકડી રે..... લાકડી રે

હે બેની તું તો મારા આંગડિયા નું ફૂલ (૨)
બેની મારી નારે ભીંજાવશો આંખડી રે
આહુડા તારા કાળજા ના કટકા કરે ચાર (૨)
બેની મારી નારી ભીજવશો આ ખડી રે
હું મને હરખ આયો વીરા તને બાંધતા રાખડી રે

હું અમે પારેવડે કાલે ઉડી જાશું
તમારો ઋણ ભઈલા ચમ કરી ચૂકવશું
હો માયા લાગેલી તારી કદી ના ભુલાશે
મારું તો ઠીક ઘરની દીવાલો પણ રડશે
હું ભઈલા જેને ભય નથી તેને કાળી રાતડી રે.... રાતડી રે

મારી લાડકી રી બેની તારા વિના કરશું કોને લાડ (૨)
એની મારી નારી ભીંજાવશો આખડી રે
આહુડા તારા કાળજા ના કટકા ચાર (૨)
બેની મારી નારી ભીંજાવશો આંખડી રે
હું આમ હરખ આયો વીરા તને બાંધતા રાખડી રે મારી લાડકી બેની મારી ભીજાવશો આંખડી રે........

snippet.title: FRUIT JELLY CAKE | Colorful Healthy Fruit Jelly Cake Recipe Making in Village | Agar Agar Jelly
snippet.description:
Today, in our village, we make colorful fruit jelly using marine algae. We use healthy fruits such as Kiwi, Muskmelon Fruit, Grapes, Green, Grapes, Pomegranate, Mango, Strawberry, Papaya, White Dragon Fruit, Red Dragon Fruit, and Watermelon.

We cool the mixture overnight and get the colorful jelly cake the following day.

Taste is Delicious!

नमस्ते दोस्तों! 
The Ranveer Show हिंदी के 192nd Episode में आप सभी का स्वागत है। आज हमारे साथ जुड़ चुके हैं Sunny Deol, जो Hindi Film Industry के Legend माने जाते हैं। हाल ही में इनकी Film Gadar 2 Release हुई है, जिसे दर्शकों से भरपूर प्यार मिल रहा है। Border, Arjun, Gadar जैसी फिल्मों में इनकी Acting को भारतीय दर्शक कभी नहीं भूल सकते हैं। 

इस Podcast में हम बात करेंगे ढ़ेर सारी बातें Sunny Deol की Early Life, Film Career, Sunny Deol की Diet, Deol Family और Success के बारे में। 

साथ ही साथ हम बात करेंगे Hindi Film Industry, Bollywood और Underworld के रिश्ते, Media Industry, Dharam Paaji, Social Media Hate और Gadar 2 की Success के बारे में और भी ढ़ेर सारी बातें। 

मैं आशा करता हूँ कि ये Video आप सभी Viewers को पसंद आएगा। खास तौर पर उन सभी को जिन्हें Bollywood और Hindi Film Industry के बारे में जानने में Interest है।

Bank Loan News का सच, Border Film की यादें और भगवान पर विश्वास जैसी चीज़ों के बारे में हम Discuss करेंगे इस Hindi Podcast में सिर्फ और सिर्फ आपके Favourite BeerBiceps Hindi Channel Ranveer Allahbadia पर।

snippet.title: मऊ रसरशीत नारळी भात | नारळीपौर्णिमा स्पेशल पारंपरिक पद्धतीने मोकळा मऊ NaraliBhat Coconut Rice Recipe
snippet.description:
सरिताज किचनची सर्व उत्पादने शुद्ध, पारंपरिक आणि केमिकल विरहित आहेत.
सरिताज किचनचे प्रॉडक्ट्स | Saritas Kitchen Products -
 1. सर्व प्रकारची लाकडी घाणा तेलं | All Types of Wood Pressed Oils
 2. डंकावर कुटून केलेला कांदा लसूण मसाला | Handmade Kanda Lasun Masala
 3. सरिताज किचन सेंद्रिय गुळ | Chemical free Jaggery cubes and powder 
 4. सेंधव मीठ | Pink Himalayan Salt
 5. सेंद्रियहळद | Organic Turmeric
ऑर्डर करण्यासाठी | To Order -
 • Website - https://saritaskitchenofficial.com/
 • Amazon - http://bitly.ws/zDuc
 
मऊ रसरशीत नारळी भात | नारळीपौर्णिमा स्पेशल पारंपरिक पद्धतीने, मोकळा मऊ नारळीभात Narali Bhat Recipe

नारळी भात | नारळी भात रेसिपी | ओल्या नारळाचा भात | नारळी पौर्णिमा स्पेशल भात | चवदार नारळी भात  | नारळी भात सरिता | गोड नारळी भात | नारळाच्या रेसिपीस | Narali Bhat | Narali Bhat Recipe | Olya Naralacha Bhat | Narali Pournima Special Rice | Tasty Coconut Rice | Narali Bhat Sarita | God Narali Bhat | Coconut Recipes | Marathi Recipes Special | Saritas Kitchen Marathi |   
 
साहित्य | Ingredients - 

भातासाठी 
• तांदूळ - १ कप | Rice – 1 cup
• तूप - २ चमचे | Ghee – 2 tsp
• लवंग - ३ ते ४ | Cloves 
• दालचिनी - १ इंच |Cinnamon – 1 inch
• हिरवी वेलची - २ ते ३ | Cardmom – 2 to 3  
• गरम पाणी - २ कप | Hot water – 2 cup 
• मीठ - चवीप्रमाणे | Salt – As per taste 
• लिंबू रस - १ चमचा | Lemon Juice – 1 tsp 
• नारळ - गुळ शिजवण्यासाठी | Coconut and Jaggery for cooking 
• तूप - २ चमचे |Ghee – 2 tsp
• गुळ - ३/४ कप | Jaggery – ¾ cup
• नारळ - १ कप | Coconut – 1 cup
• काजू बदामचे काप | Chopped Cashewnuts and Almonds 
• पिस्ते | Pistachios

Coconut Rice Recipe – 

• Soak rice for half an hour. 
• In a kadhai add ghee, cloves, cinnamon and rice and saute.
• Add water, lemon juice and salt as per taste. Let them boil.
• After boiling on high heat let water to reduce.
• Some water left then cook this on low heat. 
• After cooked allow the vapor to go out and do not cover. 
• In another pan, add ghee and let jaggery melts and saute.  
• Then add grated coconut and saute this for 2 to 3 minutes.
• In that ready rice add this mixture and saute with hands slowly.
• Let cover and cook on low heat for the 2 minutes.
• In the last add dryfruits.
• Traditional and sweet rice is now ready to eat.
 

Other Recipes –

मऊ रसरशीत नारळी भात | नारळीपौर्णिमा स्पेशल पारंपरिक पद्धतीने, मोकळा मऊ नारळीभात Narali Bhat Recipe

नारळी भात | नारळी भात रेसिपी | ओल्या नारळाचा भात | नारळी पौर्णिमा स्पेशल भात | चवदार नारळी भात  | नारळी भात सरिता | गोड नारळी भात | नारळाच्या रेसिपीस | Narali Bhat | Narali Bhat Recipe | Olya Naralacha Bhat | Narali Pournima Special Rice | Tasty Coconut Rice | Narali Bhat Sarita | God Narali Bhat | Coconut Recipes | Marathi Recipes Special | Saritas Kitchen Marathi |   
 
साहित्य | Ingredients - 

भातासाठी 
• तांदूळ - १ कप | Rice – 1 cup
• तूप - २ चमचे | Ghee – 2 tsp
• लवंग - ३ ते ४ | Cloves 
• दालचिनी - १ इंच |Cinnamon – 1 inch
• हिरवी वेलची - २ ते ३ | Cardmom – 2 to 3  
• गरम पाणी - २ कप | Hot water – 2 cup 
• मीठ - चवीप्रमाणे | Salt – As per taste 
• लिंबू रस - १ चमचा | Lemon Juice – 1 tsp 
• नारळ - गुळ शिजवण्यासाठी | Coconut and Jaggery for cooking 
• तूप - २ चमचे |Ghee – 2 tsp
• गुळ - ३/४ कप | Jaggery – ¾ cup
• नारळ - १ कप | Coconut – 1 cup
• काजू बदामचे काप | Chopped Cashewnuts and Almonds 
• पिस्ते | Pistachios

Coconut Rice Recipe – 

• Soak rice for half an hour. 
• In a kadhai add ghee, cloves, cinnamon and rice and saute.
• Add water, lemon juice and salt as per taste. Let them boil.
• After boiling on high heat let water to reduce.
• Some water left then cook this on low heat. 
• After cooked allow the vapor to go out and do not cover. 
• In another pan, add ghee and let jaggery melts and saute.  
• Then add grated coconut and saute this for 2 to 3 minutes.
• In that ready rice add this mixture and saute with hands slowly.
• Let cover and cook on low heat for the 2 minutes.
• In the last add dryfruits.
• Traditional and sweet rice is now ready to eat.

snippet.title: Behna Ne Bhai Ki Kalai Se (बहना ने भाई की कलाई से) With Lyrics | 2023 Raksha Bandhan Superhit  Song
snippet.description:
Song : Resham Ki Dori
Singer: Asha Bhosle, Kishore Kumar, Manna Dey, Mohammed Rafi, Suman Kalyanpur
Lyricist: Hasrat Jaipuri, Indeevar, Neeraj
Music Director: Shankarsinh Raghuwanshi, Jaikishan Dayabhai Pankal
Film Producer: T C Dewan
-------
Lyrics:
behna ne bhai ki kalai se
behna ne bhai ki kalai se pyar bandha hai
pyar ke do taar se sansar bandha hai
resham ki dori se resham ki dori se
resham ki dori se sansar bandha hai
behna ne bhai ki kalai se
behna ne bhai ki kalai se pyar bandha hai
pyar ke do taar se sansar bandha hai
resham ki dori se resham ki dori se
resham ki dori se sansar bandha hai

sundarta me jo kanhaiya hai
mamta me yashodha maiya hai
wo aur nahi dooja koi
wo to mera raja bhaiya hai
behna ne bhai ki kalai se pyar bandha hai
pyar ke do taar se sansar bandha hai
resham ki dori se resham ki dori se
resham ki dori se sansar bandha hai

mera phool hai tu talwar hai tu
meri laaj ka pehredaar hai tu
main akeli kaha is duniya me
mera saara sandar hai tu
behna ne bhai ki kalai se pyar bandha hai
pyar ke do taar se sansar bandha hai
resham ki dori se resham ki dori se
resham ki dori se sansar bandha hai

hume door bhale kismat kar de
apne man se na juda karna
saawan ke paawan din bhaiya
behna ko yaad kiya karna
behna ne bhai ki kalai se pyar bandha hai
pyar ke do taar se sansar bandha hai
resham ki dori se resham ki dori se
resham ki dori se sansar bandha hai
------

Ehraam-e-Junoon Episode 35 - [Eng Sub] - Neelam Muneer - Imran Abbas - Digitally Presented by Sandal Beauty Cream - 29th August 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Ehraam-e-Junoon Digitally Presented by Sandal Beauty Cream

"Ehraam-e-Junoon" follows the story of a young and immensely beautiful girl named Shanzay, who is filled with pride and stubbornness due to her upper-class upbringing. Shanzay believes that money can buy everything, including happiness. 

Despite her high standards, Shanzay is yet to find a man who can impress her until she meets Shayan at an event. Shayan is a handsome young man from a middle-class family, who takes up a job as a pizza delivery boy to make ends meet. Shanzay who is immediately drawn to Shayan wants to provide him with a better lifestyle however, Shayan keeps his distance and refuses to accept any of Shanzay’s advances.

As the story unfolds, Shanzay and Shayan's paths cross again and again, and Shanzay begins to question her beliefs about love and money. Will Shayan be the one to break through Shanzay's walls of pride and stubbornness, or will she continue to chase after superficial things?

The drama serial "Ehraam-e-Junoon" promises to take viewers on a rollercoaster ride of emotions as it explores the themes of love, pride, and class differences.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3862 | 29 Aug 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3862: Gokuldham Vs. Danger Bhai
--------------------------------------------------------
Danger Bhai chooses Iyer to give the massive injection, but Iyer manages to escape. Danger Bhai and his associates are safely locked inside the house by Iyer. Everyone at Gokuldham applauds Iyer's activities. The whole Gokuldham society beats the surviving gang member and catches him in the tire. They also arm themselves in order to continue fighting the gang. Bhide receives his utensils, while Taarak receives his home items. Will the people of Gokuldham be able to defeat this fearsome gang?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3862, 29 Aug 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Ehraam-e-Junoon Episode 36 Teaser - 29th August 2023 - HAR PAL GEO
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Ehraam-e-Junoon Episode 36 Teaser - 29th August 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

"Ehraam-e-Junoon" follows the story of a young and immensely beautiful girl named Shanzay, who is filled with pride and stubbornness due to her upper-class upbringing. Shanzay believes that money can buy everything, including happiness. 

Despite her high standards, Shanzay is yet to find a man who can impress her until she meets Shayan at an event. Shayan is a handsome young man from a middle-class family, who takes up a job as a pizza delivery boy to make ends meet. Shanzay who is immediately drawn to Shayan wants to provide him with a better lifestyle however, Shayan keeps his distance and refuses to accept any of Shanzay’s advances.

As the story unfolds, Shanzay and Shayan's paths cross again and again, and Shanzay begins to question her beliefs about love and money. Will Shayan be the one to break through Shanzay's walls of pride and stubbornness, or will she continue to chase after superficial things?

The drama serial "Ehraam-e-Junoon" promises to take viewers on a rollercoaster ride of emotions as it explores the themes of love, pride, and class differences.

Writer: Jahanzeb Qamar
Director: Syed Ramish Rizvi
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Imran Abbas as Shani
Neelam Muneer as Shanzay
Nimra Khan as Sajeela
Mahmood Aslam as Kamran
Ismat Zaidi as Kulsoom
Maira Khan as Nadiya

Saqib Sameer as Khawar
Aadi Khan as Jugnu
Birjees Farooqui as Farzana
Farah Nadeem as Shakeela
Kinza Bukhari as Shazia
Mirza Rizwan as Faiq

Ehraam-e-Junoon Digitally Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream

"Ehraam-e-Junoon" follows the story of a young and immensely beautiful girl named Shanzay, who is filled with pride and stubbornness due to her upper-class upbringing. Shanzay believes that money can buy everything, including happiness. 

Despite her high standards, Shanzay is yet to find a man who can impress her until she meets Shayan at an event. Shayan is a handsome young man from a middle-class family, who takes up a job as a pizza delivery boy to make ends meet. Shanzay who is immediately drawn to Shayan wants to provide him with a better lifestyle however, Shayan keeps his distance and refuses to accept any of Shanzay’s advances.

As the story unfolds, Shanzay and Shayan's paths cross again and again, and Shanzay begins to question her beliefs about love and money. Will Shayan be the one to break through Shanzay's walls of pride and stubbornness, or will she continue to chase after superficial things?

The drama serial "Ehraam-e-Junoon" promises to take viewers on a rollercoaster ride of emotions as it explores the themes of love, pride, and class differences.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3861 | 28 Aug 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3861: Iyer Ne Saath Chodha
--------------------------------------------------------
Champaklal is enraged by Danger Bhai's constant threat and retaliates against him. When Champaklal approaches him, he trips and threatens Bhai. Everyone in Gokuldham is concerned about Champaklal. Danger Bhai alerts and orders everyone to find Dr. Hathi, but no one is able to do it. Taarak indicates to Danger Bhai that Dr. Hathi may have gone somewhere else because they were unable to find him despite a vigorous search throughout society. Later, Danger Bhai receives a massive injection and chooses to inject it into any of Gokuldham's occupants. Who will Danger Bhai go after?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3861, 28 Aug 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :

snippet.title: Neeraj Chopra rises as the Javelin's reigning champion | World Athletics Championships Budapest 2023
snippet.description:
Neeraj Chopra, the Olympic champion, has achieved a historic milestone by becoming the inaugural Indian athlete to secure a gold medal at the World Athletics Championships. He outperformed Pakistan's Arshad Nadeem in a thrilling men's javelin final, unleashing a remarkable 88.17-meter throw. 🔥🥇🏆 #NeerajChopra #worldathleticschampionships #javelin 

While Chopra claimed the gold medal in the 2021 Tokyo Olympics, he settled for a silver during last year's world championships held in the United States. 🥇🥈 #OlympicGold #WorldChampionships

Following the medal distribution and amidst the jubilant celebrations of the athletes on the track, Chopra extended a friendly gesture by inviting Nadeem to join him for a photograph. The two competitors stood closely, with arms draped around each other in a display of sportsmanship and camaraderie. 📸🤝 #Sportsmanship #AthleteBonding"

A game-changing moment emerged in 2008 when India's Chandrayaan-1 mission unveiled an astonishing find: water on the moon's surface. This groundbreaking revelation reignited the world's fascination with lunar exploration, triggering an international craze that saw major players like China, the United States, and Israel join the pursuit. Fast forward to today, and India takes centre stage once more with Chandrayaan 3, its third lunar mission. This determined effort follows a setback experienced during the Chandrayaan 2 mission in 2019, showcasing India's unwavering commitment to unravelling the moon's mysteries. snippet.title: Dil Hi Toh Hai (Season 2) Episode 8 | Falling apart | Yogita Bihani, Karan Kundra
snippet.description:
DIL HI TOH HAI SEASON 2
Love Aur Hate Ka Second Take
In Dil Hi Toh Hai Season 2, six years after Ritwik & Palak’s separation, Ritwik’s younger brother Shivam returns from London for the first time to find that Mamta is terminally ill and his family is not together anymore. Meanwhile, Ritwik is living with his family but has lost faith in love. Palak is now a single mother with twin daughters. The only thing common is that the lead characters, Ritwik-Palak both hate each other. On Mamta’s instructions, Shivam sets out on a mission to bring Ritwik & Palak back together. Will their love win over their hate for each other? Will Shivam succeed? Catch the second season of Dil Hi Toh Hai starring Karan Kundrra & Yogita Bihani on ALTT.

snippet.description:

Episode 94: Baalveer Ki Family
-------------------------------------------------
Baalveer eventually obtains the antidote from Aageel and saves the Earth from the fatal virus. Navya and Dadaji have been cured, and the Bharadwaj family is overjoyed. Kaashvi realizes that Baalveer's victory over Aageel enabled this. Dada Ji and Navya later fail to recognize Veer and label him an invader. Maha Mahim Uttan informs Baalveer that his role on Dharti Lok has been fulfilled, and he must now return to Shashvan Lok, which is why the Bharadwaj family's memories of him have been wiped. Baalveer shares his sorrow about his estrangement from his family.

Produced By - Vipul D Shah

The new season of Baalveer follows the journey of the 24-year-old superhero who draws strength from his mother. The season revolves around his journey from Veer to Baalveer, regaining his identity and the world he belongs to with the help of partner Kaashvi.

snippet.title: Chandrayaan 3 Landing Live: ISRO's Chandrayaan-3 Mission Vikram rover soft landing on Moon
snippet.description:
#chandrayaan3 #chandrayaan3landing #isro 
 
भारतीय अंतरिक्ष एजेंसी (ISRO) द्वारा निर्मित चंद्रयान-3 के विक्रम लूनर रोवर के चंद्रमा की सतह पर बुधवार को सफलतापूर्वक उतर गया। भारत दुनिया का पहला देश है जिसने चंद्रमा के दक्षिण ध्रुव पर लूनर रोवर भेजने में सफलता प्राप्त की है। इस अवसर पर पीएण नरेन्द्र मोदी ने इसरो के वैज्ञानिकों एवं देशवासियों को  सम्बोधित करते हुए कहा, " जब हम अपनी आंखों के सामने ऐसा इतिहास बनते हुए देखते हैं, तो जीवन धन्य हो जाता है। ऐसी ऐतिहासिक घटनाएं, राष्ट्र जीवन की चिरिंजीव चेतना बन जाती हैं। ये पल अविस्मरणीय है। ये क्षण अभूतपूर्व है। ये क्षण, विकसित भारत के शंखनाद का है। ये क्षण, नए भारत के जयघोष का है। ये क्षण, मुश्किलों के महासागर को पार करने का है। ये क्षण, जीत के चंद्रपथ पर चलने का है। ये क्षण, 140 करोड़ धड़कनों के सामर्थ्य का है। ये क्षण, भारत में नई ऊर्जा, नया विश्वास, नईं चेतना का है। ये क्षण, भारत के उदयीमान भाग्य के आह्वान का है। अमृतकाल की प्रथम प्रभा में सफलता की ये अमृतवर्षा हुई है। हमने धरती पर संकल्प लिया, और चाँद पर उसे साकार किया। और हमारे वैज्ञानिक साथियों ने भी कहा कि India is now on the moon. आज हम अन्तरिक्ष में नए भारत की नई उड़ान के साक्षी बने हैं।"

#चंद्रयान_3 #vikramlander #pmmodi #narendramodi #modi 

पीएम मोदी ने वैज्ञानिकों एवं देशवासियों से कहा, "मैं टीम चंद्रयान को, इसरो को और देश के सभी वैज्ञानिकों को जी जान से बहुत-बहुत बधाई देता हूँ, जिन्होंने इस पल के लिए वर्षों तक इतना परिश्रम किया है। उत्साह, उमंग, आनंद और भावुकता से भरे इस अद्भुत पल के लिए मैं 140 करोड़ देशवासियों को भी कोटि-कोटि बधाइयाँ देता हूँ!"

पीएम मोदी ने आगे कहा, "हमारे वैज्ञानिकों के परिश्रम और प्रतिभा से भारत, चंद्रमा के उस दक्षिणी ध्रुव पर पहुंचा है, जहां आज तक दुनिया का कोई भी देश नहीं पहुंच सका है। अब आज के बाद से चाँद से जुड़े मिथक बदल जाएंगे, कथानक भी बदल जाएंगे, और नई पीढ़ी के लिए कहावतें भी बदल जाएंगी। भारत में तो हम सभी लोग धरती को माँ कहते हैं और चाँद को मामा बुलाते हैं। कभी कहा जाता था, चंदा मामा बहुत ‘दूर’ के हैं। अब एक दिन वो भी आएगा जब बच्चे कहा करेंगे- चंदा मामा बस एक ‘टूर’ के हैं।"

Chandrayaan 3 mission robotic lunar rover Vikram landed on the Moon today. Chandrayaan-3 is developed by Indian space Research Organization (ISRO). India's is the world's first country to land moon mission on it's south pole. India became 4th country to land on moon. Chandrayaan-3 mission was launched on July 14 on board launch vehicle MARK-III (LVM-3) rocket.

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Click here to watch all the fun episodes of Bapuji Ka Chashmah

snippet.title: World Athletics Championships 2023: Neeraj Chopra wins gold medal in Men's Javelin
snippet.description:
Neeraj Chopra achieved a historic milestone for India by securing the country's inaugural gold medal in the Men's Javelin event at the 2023 World Athletics Championships held in Budapest. Prime Minister Narendra Modi praised Neeraj Chopra's remarkable performance, expressing his admiration through a tweet. He lauded Neeraj Chopra as an embodiment of excellence, highlighting his unwavering commitment, precision, and passion. Not only is Neeraj a champion in athletics, but he also stands as an unparalleled symbol of greatness in the world of sports. The Prime Minister extended his congratulations to Neeraj Chopra for clinching the gold medal at the World Athletics Championships. Anurag Thakur, the Union Sports Minister, also joined in celebrating Neeraj Chopra's victory at the World Athletics Championships in Budapest. Through a tweet, he referred to Neeraj as the "golden boy" of Indian athletics, acknowledging his triumph in the men's javelin throw event. Anurag Thakur conveyed the nation's pride in Neeraj's accomplishments and emphasized that this significant moment would forever be etched in the annals of Indian sports history.
